<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0, viewport-fit=cover">
    <title>文章约稿 · Arseeya</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Arseeya 文章约稿服务——定制属于你的故事。同人、原创皆可，详细价目与须知。">
    <meta name="keywords" content="约稿, 文章约稿, 定制创作, Arseeya, 阿尔茜娅">
    <meta name="author" content="Arseeya">
    <meta name="robots" content="index, follow">

    <!-- Open Graph -->
    <meta property="og:title" content="文章约稿 · Arseeya">
    <meta property="og:description" content="定制属于你的故事。">
    <meta property="og:type" content="website">
    <meta property="og:url" content="https://arseeya.link/commission.html">
    <meta property="og:image" content="https://arseeya.link/hero.jpg">

    <!-- 字体与基础样式 -->
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0f0c1f 0%, #1a1a2e 50%, #16213e 100%);
            color: #e0e0e0;
            font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            min-height: 100vh;
            padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
        }

        /* 毛玻璃容器 */
        .glass-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        /* 导航栏 */
        .nav-bar {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            padding-bottom: 1rem;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .nav-links {
            display: flex;
            gap: 1.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .nav-links a {
            color: #e0e0e0;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: color 0.2s;
            font-size: 0.95rem;
        }

        .nav-links a:hover {
            color: #e94560;
        }

        .back-home {
            background: rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.2);
            padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.4);
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .back-home:hover {
            background: #e94560;
            color: white !important;
        }

        /* 标题区 */
        .hero {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
        }

        .hero h1 {
            font-size: 2.8rem;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #e94560);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }

        .hero p {
            color: #a0a0b0;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* 章节卡片通用样式 */
        .section {
            background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 1.8rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }

        .section h2 {
            font-size: 1.6rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.2rem;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 0.6rem;
            color: #e94560;
            border-left: 3px solid #e94560;
            padding-left: 1rem;
        }

        /* 流程卡片网格 */
        .steps-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.5rem;
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }

        .step-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
            border-radius: 1.2rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            transition: all 0.2s;
        }

        .step-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .step-number {
            width: 40px;
            height: 40px;
            background: #e94560;
            border-radius: 50%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            margin: 0 auto 1rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
        }

        /* 价目表 */
        .pricing-table {
            overflow-x: auto;
        }

        .pricing-table table {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .pricing-table th,
        .pricing-table td {
            padding: 1rem;
            text-align: left;
            border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }

        .pricing-table th {
            color: #e94560;
            font-weight: 600;
        }

        .price {
            color: #e94560;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        /* 须知列表 */
        .notice-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding-left: 0;
        }

        .notice-list li {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
            padding-left: 1.5rem;
            position: relative;
        }

        .notice-list li::before {
            content: "📌";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #e94560;
        }

        /* 联系邮箱区域 */
        .contact-box {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.15), rgba(102, 126, 234, 0.15));
            border-radius: 1.5rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
        }

        .email {
            font-size: 1.8rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fff, #e94560);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            background-clip: text;
            color: transparent;
            margin: 0.5rem 0;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            background: #e94560;
            color: white;
            padding: 0.8rem 2rem;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: bold;
            transition: all 0.2s;
            border: none;
            cursor: pointer;
            margin-top: 0.5rem;
        }

        .btn:hover {
            background: #c72a4a;
            transform: scale(1.02);
            box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(233, 69, 96, 0.4);
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            border: 1px solid #e94560;
            color: #e94560;
        }

        .btn-outline:hover {
            background: #e94560;
            color: white;
        }

        /* 状态徽章 */
        .status-badge {
            display: inline-block;
            background: rgba(255, 180, 40, 0.2);
            border: 1px solid #ffb428;
            color: #ffb428;
            border-radius: 2rem;
            padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            margin-left: 1rem;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }

        footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 1.5rem;
            border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
            font-size: 0.85rem;
            color: #888;
        }

        footer a {
            color: #e94560;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            body {
                padding: 1rem;
            }
            .glass-container {
                padding: 1.2rem;
            }
            .hero h1 {
                font-size: 2rem;
            }
            .email {
                font-size: 1.2rem;
                word-break: break-all;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="glass-container">
    <!-- 导航栏 -->
    <div class="nav-bar">
        <div class="nav-links">
            <a href="/index.html">首页</a>
            <a href="/novels/听潮事记/">作品</a>
            <a href="/world.html">百科</a>
            <a href="/download.html">下载</a>
            <a href="/commission.html" style="color:#e94560;">📝 约稿</a>
        </div>
        <a href="/index.html" class="back-home">← 返回首页</a>
    </div>

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="hero">
        <h1>📝 文章约稿 <span class="status-badge">🔄 准备中</span></h1>
        <p>定制属于你的故事 — 同人、原创皆可，让文字成为独特的礼物</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 温馨提示（未开放时显示） -->
    <div style="background: rgba(255, 180, 40, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid #ffb428; padding: 1rem; border-radius: 1rem; margin-bottom: 2rem;">
        💡 <strong>当前状态：</strong> 约稿服务正在筹备中，价目表与流程仅供参考。正式开放后将以本页面公告为准。如需提前咨询，可发送邮件至下方邮箱。
    </div>

    <!-- 约稿流程 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>📋 约稿流程</h2>
        <div class="steps-grid">
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">1</div>
                <h3>沟通需求</h3>
                <p>发送邮件说明题材、字数、风格、用途等需求</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">2</div>
                <h3>确认报价</h3>
                <p>根据需求评估价格与交付时间，双方确认</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">3</div>
                <h3>支付定金</h3>
                <p>支付50%定金后开始创作</p>
            </div>
            <div class="step-card">
                <div class="step-number">4</div>
                <h3>交付修改</h3>
                <p>交付初稿，可免费修改3次，满意后付尾款</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- 价目表 -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>💰 参考价目表</h2>
        <div class="pricing-table">
            <table>
                <thead>
                    <tr>
                        <th>类型</th>
                        <th>字数范围</th>
                        <th>参考价格</th>
                        <th>预计交付</th>
                    </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                    <tr>
                        <td>短篇 · 随笔</td>
                        <td>1000~3000字</td>
                        <td class="price">¥100 ~ 250</td>
                        <td>3-5个工作日</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>短篇 · 故事</td>
                        <td>3000~8000字</td>
                        <td class="price">¥250 ~ 600</td>
                        <td>5-10个工作日</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>中篇 · 小说</td>
                        <td>8000~20000字</td>
                        <td class="price">¥600 ~ 1400</td>
                        <td>10-20个工作日</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>角色设定/小传</td>
                        <td>500~2000字</td>
                        <td class="price">¥80 ~ 200</td>
                        <td>2-4个工作日</td>
                    </tr>
                    <tr>
                        <td>世界观设定</td>
                        <td>按需协商</td>
                        <td class="price">¥200起</td>
                        <td>协商确定</td>
                    </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
        </div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.85rem; color: #aaa; margin-top: 1rem;">※ 以上为参考报价，实际价格根据题材复杂度、完成度要求浮动。同人/OC创作有优惠。</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 约稿须知（精简版，引用完整条款） -->
    <div class="section">
        <h2>📜 约稿须知</h2>
        <ul class="notice-list">
            <li><strong>版权归属：</strong> 约稿作品著作权归作者 Arseeya 所有，您获得个人非商业使用许可。具体详见 <a href="/terms.html#5.2" style="color:#e94560;">完整条款 5.2</a>。</li>
            <li><strong>修改次数：</strong> 免费修改不超过3次，超出部分按 ¥30/次 收取。</li>
            <li><strong>禁止行为：</strong> 不得将约稿作品用于商业目的、AI训练、公开发布（未经授权）或声称自己为作者。</li>
            <li><strong>退款政策：</strong> 若作者未能按约定完成，退还费用50%~100%；因用户原因中断，定金不退。</li>
            <li><strong>交付格式：</strong> 默认交付 .txt 或 .docx 文件，可免费提供 .pdf。</li>
        </ul>
        <p style="margin-top: 1rem;">📖 完整约稿条款请查阅 <a href="/terms.html#5.2" style="color:#e94560;" target="_blank">《完整网站使用条款》第5.2条</a>。</p>
    </div>

    <!-- 联系邮箱区域 -->
    <div class="contact-box">
        <p>✉️ 联系约稿</p>
        <div class="email">le.arseeya@outlook.com</div>
        <p style="font-size: 0.9rem; margin-top: 0.5rem;">请将以下信息连同您的需求一起发送邮件：</p>
        <ul style="display: inline-block; text-align: left; margin-top: 0.8rem; color: #ccc;">
            <li>• 期望题材/世界观</li>
            <li>• 预估字数</li>
            <li>• 用途（个人收藏/展示/礼物等）</li>
            <li>• 交付期限要求</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <a href="mailto:le.arseeya@outlook.com?subject=文章约稿咨询&body=您好，我想咨询文章约稿：%0D%0A%0D%0A题材：%0D%0A字数：%0D%0A用途：%0D%0A期望交付时间：%0D%0A%0D%0A其他说明：" class="btn">📧 邮件联系约稿</a>
    </div>

    <!-- 返回导航辅助 -->
    <div style="text-align: center; margin-top: 1rem;">
        <a href="/index.html" class="btn-outline btn" style="background: transparent;">← 返回首页</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>© Arseeya（阿尔茜娅）. All Rights Reserved. | 约稿专用邮箱：le.arseeya@outlook.com</p>
        <p><a href="/terms.html">完整条款</a> | <a href="/about.html">关于 Arseeya</a></p>
    </footer>
</div>

<script>
    // 简单的页面淡入效果（可选）
    document.body.style.opacity = '0';
    document.body.style.transition = 'opacity 0.3s';
    window.addEventListener('load', () => {
        document.body.style.opacity = '1';
    });
</script>
</body>
</html>